# Nicholas Martinez - M3 Portfolio

## Areas of Emphasis

My goal throughout the module has been to work through the material with a focus on Development Operations and deployment. I have spent a significant amount of time working with AWS, Capistrano and Chef. During our Cloney Island project, I was able to deploy our app out to an AWS EC2 instance with S3 storage and built in download and upload functionality into the our Drop Box clone.

