(Project was not evaluated)

#### (SpamGrid)

* [GitHub URL](https://github.com/NZenitram/spamgrid)

For the personal project this module I set out to build a web application that sends 'spam' email. The goal of this project was to build an app that allowed a user to upload a list of email addresses, select an email template, and send mass emails to their victims while circumventing the anti-spam features use by SendGrid.

When a user clicks 'send spam' the application is able to spin up an EC2 instance on AWS, deploy the application, send the emails and shut the server down. This give each new iteration of email sent a fresh IP.

